{"about_the_game":"<strong>Sinned Arena</strong> is a classic arena shooter inspired by timeless 90s games. You are trapped in Hell with other unfortunate souls, fighting among each other for demons twisted pleasures. Fight for your way out of this dark place but beware, demons aren't there just to watch.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Single player</h2><br>Engage in Single player in two different ways:<br>Play <strong>Campaign</strong> mode where you go through predefined Deathmatch maps with progressively increasing difficulty of your opponents.<br>Play <strong>Skirmish</strong> mode where you can tailor the gameplay experience to your liking. You can choose game mode, map, score goal, number of opponents and their skills. You can also spice up your experience with Mutators that are adding various modifiers to the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789980/extras/fight2.gif?t=1740330888\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game modes</h2><br>The game offers 5 game modes: <strong>Deathmatch</strong>, <strong>Team Deathmatch</strong>, <strong>Heartcore</strong>, <strong>Instagib</strong> and <strong>Team Instagib</strong><br><br>Deathmatch is a classic Free For All mode, where you are winning by being first to get required amount of kills.<br>Team Deathmatch is a team variant of Deathmatch mode where goal is again reaching required amount of kills but score of your teammates counts as well.<br><br>Heartcore is a team mode where goal is to destroy a heart inside of enemy base. First team to destroy enemy heart wins.<br><br>Instagib a Team Instagib are similar to Deathmatch or Team Deatchmatch modes but this time, you only have one weapon at your disposal and it turns your opponents into bunch of gibs with a single shot.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2789980/extras/heartcore3.gif?t=1740330888\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Progression system</h2><br>Thro